{"tid":1981142,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"紐西蘭外交部關注香港民主派被捕 事件令人非常失望","createTime":"2020-04-20T13:18:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-20T13:19:31.000Z","uid":70063,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"74363cd67d95d4730d4b97e1d8abef137a94cad4","tid":1981142,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T13:18:54.000Z","msg":"警方週六（18日）拘捕 15 名民主派人士，包括民主黨創黨主席李柱銘、公民黨立法會前議員吳靄儀等。紐西蘭外交部長彼特斯(Winston Peters)，今在官方新聞稿表示關注事件，「包括立法會議員在內，共有 15 名備受矚目的民主派人士被捕，事件令人十分失望」。他又強調，在《基本法》的保障下，所有市民理應享受言論及集會自由。<br />\n<br />\n新聞稿交代指，香港警察在週六拘捕 15 名民主派人士，指他們涉嫌在去年的反修例運動中，組織或參與未經許可集會。被捕者包括民主黨創黨主席李柱銘、職工盟領袖李卓人。彼特斯重申，對事件感到十分失望，特別是在這個國際理應合作對抗大流行疫症的時刻。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/4-18-%E5%A4%A7%E6%90%9C%E6%8D%95-%E7%B4%90%E8%A5%BF%E8%98%AD%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%A4%E9%83%A8%E9%97%9C%E6%B3%A8%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E6%B4%BE%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95-%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6%E4%BB%A4%E4%BA%BA%E9%9D%9E%E5%B8%B8%E5%A4%B1%E6%9C%9B/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F4-18-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%2590%259C%25E6%258D%2595-%25E7%25B4%2590%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E8%2598%25AD%25E5%25A4%2596%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E9%2583%25A8%25E9%2597%259C%25E6%25B3%25A8%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%25B0%2591%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595-%25E4%25BA%258B%25E4%25BB%25B6%25E4%25BB%25A4%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%259D%259E%25E5%25B8%25B8%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E6%259C%259B%2F&d=1E6MrqGGcFSEGQF%2FdL0KzaVJa0bF76%2FliPNifPMhSX0%3D&h=c4d36cd3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F4-18-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%2590%259C%25E6%258D%2595-%25E7%25B4%2590%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E8%2598%25AD%25E5%25A4%2596%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E9%2583%25A8%25E9%2597%259C%25E6%25B3%25A8%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%25B0%2591%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595-%25E4%25BA%258B%25E4%25BB%25B6%25E4%25BB%25A4%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%259D%259E%25E5%25B8%25B8%25